<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to <%= companyName %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #163C6C 0%, #1A80AA 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .greeting p {
      margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    }
    .credentials-box {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-left: 4px solid #1A80AA;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .credentials-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #163C6C;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .credential-item {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .credential-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #163C6C;
      display: inline-block;
      min-width: 120px;
    }
    .credential-value {
      color: #333;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .login-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #1A80AA;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #163C6C;
    }
    .support-section {
      background-color: #f0f7ff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    .support-section p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 4px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to <%= companyName %></h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">
          <p>Hi <%= userName %>,</p>
          <p>Your account has been successfully created on the accounting system. You can now access all the tools and features you need to manage your financial tasks efficiently.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Credentials -->
        <div class="credentials-box">
          <h3>🔐 Your Login Information</h3>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <span class="credential-label">Email:</span>
            <span class="credential-value"><%= userEmail %></span>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <span class="credential-label">Password:</span>
            <span class="credential-value"><%= temporaryPassword %></span>
          </div>
          <p class="login-note">⚠️ We strongly recommend changing your password after your first login for security purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Login Button -->
        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Sign In to Your Account</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Getting Started Info -->
        <div class="support-section">
          <p><strong>📌 Getting Started:</strong></p>
          <p>1. Use your email and temporary password to log in</p>
          <p>2. Navigate to your account settings to change your password</p>
          <p>3. Explore the dashboard to familiarize yourself with the system</p>
          <p>4. Contact your administrator if you need any assistance</p>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or experience any issues accessing your account, please don't hesitate to reach out to your system administrator for support.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br><strong><%= companyName %> Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
